= BComposer

== Introduction

The bulletin composer, list management, and delivery utility.

Bcomposer was designed initially with a simple need, to be able to create
complex email bulletins, and allow anyone to add contents to them easily
and quickly. A templating system is provided using Liquid templates (and
optionally ERB) so that bulletin contents can be stored in the database
an manipulated easily.

As the system has development, more features have been added such as 
subscription forms used by the subscribers, support for groups of projects 
sharing access to the subscribers, and statistics.

