== Key Features

The following components make up the current version of BComposer:

 * Projects
 * Project Groups - A project belongs to one of these.
 * User access restrictions - limit access to certain users based by project
and function; templates for example can be accessed by designers, but not by 
the content editors.
 * Bulletins are split into seccions and sections into entries - this allows 
a template to be split into parts allowing complex layouts to be edited
easily.
 * Templating
 ** Liquid template language (also ERB, but not recommended)
 ** Used for: Bulletins, subscription emails and internal pages
 ** A set of default templates are provided.
 * Statistics - support for hidden images recording access by single users.

